channel.title: I need a Developer for my game! ~many reasons~
channel.description:
Hey if any of you know about coding a 317 that loads a 525 I am asking that you might be able to help me with my rsps. Contact me on skype, email, youtube channel, or pm me. My Skype name is: "Dylan.laflamme" / and what i use for my skype name is "Dylan.Stafford" My youtube channel: Zipper643 My email: zipper643@hotmail.com My name on here : Zipper643 Forums: Zipperscape.netne.net

(Were using paypal) Were saving up for a VPS and we don;t have a webclient yet!! :( We do not know how to make one... :L if anyone does know how to make a webclient pleassseeeeee let me know ASAP!!! (we need some more developers!) Thanks!!
